name xcolor
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Driver-independent color extensions for LaTeX and pdfLaTeX
longdesc The package starts from the basic facilities of the color
longdesc package, and provides easy driver-independent access to several
longdesc kinds of color tints, shades, tones, and mixes of arbitrary
longdesc colors. It allows a user to select a document-wide target color
longdesc model and offers complete tools for conversion between eight
longdesc color models. Additionally, there is a command for alternating
longdesc row colors plus repeated non-aligned material (like horizontal
longdesc lines) in tables. Colors can be mixed like
longdesc \color{red!30!green!40!blue}.
